<body>

<div class="about-container">

    <h1 class="about-title">
        About SitApp
    </h1>

    <div class="about-section">

        <h2>What is SitApp?</h2>

        <p>

            SitApp is a modern educational and social learning platform created to help students learn, practice objective questions, access academic materials, interact with others, and grow academically through technology.

            The platform combines education, communication, video sharing, and interactive learning tools into one complete system for students and learners.

        </p>

    </div>

    <div class="about-section">

        <h2>How To Use SitApp</h2>

        <ul>

            <li>Create an account and login securely.</li>

            <li>Select your academic level and department.</li>

            <li>Access objective quizzes and past questions.</li>

            <li>View answers and explanations for educational purposes.</li>

            <li>Upload educational videos and learning content.</li>

            <li>Chat and interact with other students.</li>

            <li>Search for subjects easily using the search feature.</li>

            <li>Access both Primary and JHS educational materials.</li>

        </ul>

    </div>

    <div class="about-section">

        <h2>Benefits of SitApp</h2>

        <ul>

            <li>Easy access to academic resources.</li>

            <li>Interactive objective quiz system.</li>

            <li>Educational video sharing.</li>

            <li>Improved learning experience for students.</li>

            <li>Fast and modern mobile-friendly design.</li>

            <li>Supports collaboration between students.</li>

            <li>Helps students prepare for examinations effectively.</li>

            <li>Provides categorized educational content.</li>

        </ul>

    </div>

    <div class="about-section">

        <h2>Community Rules & Policies</h2>

        <ul>

            <li>No explicit, violent, or inappropriate content is allowed.</li>

            <li>No hate speech, bullying, harassment, or discrimination.</li>

            <li>Users must not upload copyrighted materials illegally.</li>

            <li>Educational content should remain respectful and lawful.</li>

            <li>Spamming, scams, or fake accounts are prohibited.</li>

            <li>Users must not attempt to hack or damage the platform.</li>

            <li>Violation of policies may lead to suspension or permanent bans.</li>

        </ul>

    </div>

    <div class="about-section">

        <h2>Copyright Policy</h2>

        <p>

            All educational materials, designs, logos, software systems, and platform structures within SitApp are protected under copyright laws.

            Users are not permitted to copy, reproduce, distribute, or sell SitApp content without authorization.

            Educational materials uploaded by users remain the responsibility of the uploader.

        </p>

    </div>

    <div class="about-section">

        <h2>Future Updates</h2>

        <ul>

            <li>Realtime WhatsApp-style messaging.</li>

            <li>Group chats and voice calls.</li>

            <li>AI-powered unsafe content detection.</li>

            <li>Video comments and reactions.</li>

            <li>Followers and social interaction system.</li>

            <li>Live educational classes.</li>

            <li>Dark mode support.</li>

            <li>Push notifications.</li>

            <li>AI study assistant.</li>

            <li>Video monetization system.</li>

        </ul>

    </div>

    <div class="founder-box">

        <h2>Founder & CEO</h2>

        <h1>CRAYNER PRINCE</h1>

        <p>
            Creator of SitApp Educational Platform
        </p>

